40|$|AbstractThis {{document}} mainly {{outlines the}} procedures on implementation {{of control of}} S 3 C 2440 based embedded Linux <b>stepping</b> <b>motor.</b> Such discussion is focused on hardware design method, driving program compilation and application program compilation. It also introduces the concept of <b>stepping</b> <b>motor</b> control and analyzes structure, compilation procedure and improvement of <b>stepping</b> <b>motor</b> driving program in embedded system. Application of S 3 C 2440 and Linux 2. 6. 30 based driving program can realize various controls by ARM processor of <b>stepping</b> <b>motor</b> in embedded Linux system...|$|R
